Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和新教科书有一拼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
