Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特等席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去陌生城镇的陌生学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下站是梦丘商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦丘商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火鸟老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀老师在刚才的公交上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就在你身后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你 不直接坐公交到学校前面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天起得早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要走超棒的路线上学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超棒路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是能充分感受早晨的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么火鸟老师也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你知道这路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师每天都走这条路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是在时间富裕的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟最适合悠闲散步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是早上的治愈时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,1396,0,0,,{\fs48\bord0\shad0\frz13\an4\1c&H2B2B2B&}千鹤\N──────────\N早上好-！\N别迟到了哦双叶-！\N还有，骑电动车时一定要\N安全驾驶！\N\N千鹤 上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.86,Default,NTP,1396,0,500,,{\fs48\bord0\shad0\frz13\an4\1c&H2B2B2B&}千鹤\NRe:早上好-！\N\N我出门了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是这条路线的最佳景点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里跑是熟练水肺潜水员级的难度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种难关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用年轻气盛来决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我这边就用大人的力量来决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真赶时间啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 并没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许早上就热血过头了一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 没事吗 小日向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚实在是麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你在说什么我完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面完全不良好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别从那种地方搞正面直立入水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 知道正面直立入水就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火鸟老师难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有潜水员同伴是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别再那么乱来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 今天就到这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周开始就是上一整天6节课了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还有
