Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当三年归宅部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要去哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和校门方向相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我那个绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是水肺潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潜水员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 火鸟老师说过体验入部是从下周开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便进去的话会被训的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来小茶是这里的部员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为耳朵与尾巴是茶色的所以叫小茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢给人起绰号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茶不是部员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是潜水部的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 应该不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为早春外面还很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才进来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在意潜水服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得有点儿帅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水服有各种设计和款式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但基本能分成两大类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干式和湿式两种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿式潜水服是以水进入衣服里为前提的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干式潜水服里面是干的完全防水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全防水 要怎么做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿一下看看比较容易说明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对我反对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会被训的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点 帮我拉下后面的拉链
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有手腕这里和脖子是开口的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里用松紧带紧紧勒住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水是进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水不会从这拉链处进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说这拉链和宇航服上用的是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航服 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗略来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是暖和的时候穿湿式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷的时候穿干式的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便在这周边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7月到9月的三个月间是湿式潜水服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解得真细致呢 小日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为感兴趣 一直在潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点要不要也稍微试穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一下就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多这个码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉逐渐被带进小日向同学的步调里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合适很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 穿上之后的感想是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离校舍远谁都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且新学期一早不会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 肚子疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样拉开脖子这里蹲下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气就会一下子出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点也做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子贴身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事吗 小日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微排出些空气也不会沉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别让我担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 要来吗 茶顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从刚才开始一直被小日向同学的步调牵着走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净做了些以平常的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本无法想像的大胆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新世界相遇的同学闪闪发光着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看着这非常有趣的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中欢欣雀跃的上升气流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会将我的身体拋入天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然最开始只能听到自己的呼吸声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那会逐渐溶入海中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉分不清到哪里是自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里是大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家真是从海里诞生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便说的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点要不要也—起来潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早之所以比昨天更想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为有这孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我稍微考虑一下吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//===============NEXT===============
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是在什么都没有的地方也潜藏着乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以每一天都充满着有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集蓝海少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢欣雀跃与幸福秘诀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢欣雀跃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢欣雀跃
